phrases: Figure skating is the beautiful winter sport everyone loves!
How dare you use it as a weapon to hurt an innocent girl?!
In the name of my favorite skaters, Katarina Witt and Midori Ito,
Sailor Moon is going to punish you, okay?!
I am sorry I am not straightforward, I can say it in my dreams
My thoughts are about to short circuit, I want to see you right now
Moonlight that makes me want to cry, midnight that keeps me from calling
Because I am so innocent, what should I do?
Guided by the light of the moon
We will meet again and again
I count the sparkle of constellations to foretell the future of my love
We were born in the same land, miracle romance
I believe in it, miracle romance
You can tell why Janelyn and Misha are Olympic gold medallists.
But if she likes figure skating,
maybe she is becoming more aware of herself as the princess.
After all, figure skating was the most popular sport
in the world of the moon.
The princess's skating was especially beautiful!
I guess I was gifted with a lot of talent!
If I use this sport, supposedly the most popular
among the girls on the moon...
You could lure Sailor Moon out
and finally take the Silver Crystal away from her.
Is that what you are saying?
and stake your honor on this makeshift trap?
If you are a proud warrior,
should you not attack your enemy head on?
A battle is meaningless without a victory.
If you had not interfered unnecessarily,
we would already have the Silver Crystal in our hands!
Heh, I would not know about that.
Kunzite, you may set that plan into motion immediately.
What kind of timing was that on that jump?!
That is enough practice for today!
Janelyn, I thought we were Olympic gold medallists!
I am going to go look for a new partner!
I cannot allow you to break up.
You two have been given a mission,
and that is to work for the Dark Kingdom.
I had no idea we had a skating rink like this.
And to commemorate its opening, the Olympic gold medallists,
Janelyn and Misha are going to coach us!
But, so, why did we have to come, too?
I have an open national mock exam tomorrow,
so I need to go home to study.
Oh, the thing is... so I need to go home to study.
Only groups of five girls get in free!
It makes you want to check it out, does not it?!
It is one of those, Ask, and you shall be answered, things!
Should not that be, Ask, and you shall receive?
Should not that be, Ask, and you shall receive?
It does not matter which it is!
Come on, let us go ask!
They are all just here out of curiosity.
Brings back memories, does not it?
Oh, it is the usual pattern.
She certainly delivers, does not she?
Let us all have fun today, skating together!
No matter what you are doing, the basics are important.
The first step is getting used to the ice.
Then, since you are an energetic group,
come on out into the rink first.
I still do not have my skates on!
Rei's being mean to me again!
Rei's being mean to me again!
Is this your first time skating?
After all, I was an expert at this on the moon world!
I am going to do it, too!
Usagi, time for your brilliant debut!
This is not how it is supposed to go...
I am not going to expect a lot out of Usagi.
Sailor Jupiter was also an expert,
considered to be as good as the princess.
Now, everyone, let us all skate!
Find Sailor Moon through her athletic abilities and agility.
Does it look like it will work?
My judgment as an Olympic gold medallist is flawless.
However, you have never actually met the sailor warriors.
Do not let you guard down.
Sailor Moon is known to be a superb warrior.
They say she has a clumsy side, but this is out of the question.
Wonderful girl, would you please skate with me?
Excuse me, if you would like, I am free any time to be...
It looks exactly like my senior at school who broke my heart.
She lifted a man up into the air...
It is a technique no one in the world has accomplished yet!
Misha, how could you pass over me?!
Were you serious about breaking up?!
Today's free lesson is now over.
Everyone, please leave the rink and go home immediately.
Excuse me, I have to go home now.
I will not let you go.
You are the best partner for me in the world.
I hope they do it again.
But at least we got to see them in person.
The coach is giving her a special lesson.
Usagi was with us until just a minute ago.
Could it really have been another trap set by the Dark Kingdom?!
And I run swiftly over here.
And I run swiftly over here.
Only I cannot just back down and go home!
Only I am going to get them to give me lessons, too!
I am going to get them to give me lessons, too!
That girl is skating so nimbly with my Misha!
Do not tell me this is...
You must have had some figure skating experience.
Will not you tell me the truth?
Misha, so you and I are really over, are not we?!
If I have to give you up to an amateur like that,
Do not jump to conclusions, Janelyn!
I was just trying to find out whether she was Sailor Moon!
It is true, her technique is first class,
but you cannot form a pair based solely on that!
Come with me, Misha, my partner.
We are the best pair in the world!
Together, we are the Zoyrin Geller!
Now that you have seen us,
we cannot let you return alive!
I am a sailor warrior of love and justice, Sailor Moon!
We will deliver the finishing blow!
How dare you use graceful figure skating as a weapon
Sailor Moon will not let you get away with it!
In the name of the moon, I will punish you!
We have been waiting for you!
The Silver Crystal will be ours!
I will not let you have it!
I cannot skate, even when I am transformed?!
I just do not like their underhanded method,
which has dragged an innocent bystander into this mess.
After I have brought the monsters under control,
I will return for the Silver Crystal.
Master Endymion, your help is not necessary!
We will not hold back, even for you!
Do you think you could win in a fight against me?
I think it would be better if you did not taunt them.
Have a taste of the techniques of gold medallists!
I jumped all on my own!
Go back to who you were!
So, you are all here, sailor warriors.
This is the icy hell of absolute zero temperature.
Once you have all turned into ice figures,
I will return and take my sweet time getting the Silver Crystal.
I cannot hold out much longer!
I cannot hold out much longer!
Do not think my feelings have been hurt!
I am not going to let it bother me!
Man, I better just find another nice guy soon and...
looks just like my senior at school who broke my heart!
During the day, the fragrance of flowers
During the night, the twinkle of the stars
It is a world no one knows about
And there lives a princess, dreaming of a sweet kiss
Offer a prayer to the moon
It will surely bring you happiness
Go round and round, the moon's merry-go-round
Make that serene dress made of glass flutter in the wind
She is always watching over us
